SONDAG 13 November Kerssangdiens by NG Moedergemeente om 19:00. Bring asb n kers in n blaker saam. U word ook vriendelik versoek om n lekker bederfie vir minderbevoorregtes saam te bring. Ons wil hul harte met n spesiale geskenkie tydens Kerstyd verbly. Deuroffer: Diens van Barmhartigheid. DONDERDAG 17 November Alzheimer-ondersteuningsgroep se laaste vergadering vir 2016: Bain Laversaal, Millennium-park om 15:00. Kom gesels oor n koppie tee oor idees vir volgende jaar. Kontak Christine Nelson (073 366 3216). Bring asb n donasie ten bate van Alzheimer SA. FRIDAY 18 November Luna Paige performs at The Showroom Theatre in Prince Albert at 20:00. Luna Paige is a songwriter who accompanies herself on the piano and the guitar and has her own unique way of weaving her own and other s stories into her music Tickets (R130) can be booked online: www. showroomtheatre.co.za. Tel 023 541 1563. SATERDAG 19 November HipHopFreaks Youth Development hou n rym-kletskonsert in die Nicolonia Saal, Bridgton, om 17:00 om fondse in te samel vir n Kersete vir minderbevoorregte kinders. n Gelukkige trekking met wonderlike pryse sal gehou word. Kaartjies teen R10 n enkel- en R15 n dubbelkaartjie. R20 by die deur. Kontak Farren Campher by 062 477 2100 vir verdere navrae. SATERDAG 26 November Volmoed Vleisfees. 10:00 (kiosk open reeds 09:00) by Volmoed Kerksaal. Lam, steak, maalvleis, wors en patties. Hamburgers, pannekoek, poeding ens by kiosk beskikbaar. Navrae: Clara Mulder (084 504 3377)&nbsp; Name (required) Mail (will not be published) (required) Website Your email address will not be published. Required fields are marked * Comment Name * Email * Website